              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Guidance updated to address the lifting of the national restrictions from 2 December 2020. Amendments to key policy areas have been made to reflect the local restriction tiers.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-11-20T11:09:14.000+00:00">20 November 2020</time>
